<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Pending | Boli Bazar</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: '#d90429',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 font-sans min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">

    <div class="bg-white rounded-[40px] shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-10 max-w-lg w-full text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-600"></div>
        
        <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-hourglass-half text-4xl text-blue-500 animate-pulse"></i>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-4">Application Under Review</h1>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Thank you for applying to be a Boli Bazar Sales Executive! Your application has been received and is currently waiting for admin approval. 
            Once approved, you will be assigned a unique Executive Code to start onboarding retailers.
        </p>

        <a href="/login" class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200 font-black text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition">
            Back to Login
        </a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
